      <p>
        <indexentry>Agility</indexentry>
        <indexentry>Abilities<subentry>Agility</subentry></indexentry>
        <indexentry>Acrobatics (use Agility)</indexentry>
        The characters ability to move easily; their nimbleness, athleticism and dexterity.
        Agility modifies the characters Dodge Checks.	
      </p>

      <p>
	The Sure-Feet specialization is used when the attacker the character would be knocked
	prone.
      </p>      
