    <specializations>
      <specialization>Listen</specialization>
      <specialization>Smell</specialization>
      <specialization>Scout</specialization>
    </specializations>
    <abilitydescription>
      <p>
        <indexentry>Perception</indexentry>
        <indexentry>Abilities<subentry>Perception</subentry></indexentry>
        <indexentry>Spot Hidden<subentry>use Perception</subentry></indexentry>
        <indexentry>Initiative<subentry>see Perception</subentry></indexentry>
        <indexentry>Notice (use Perception)</indexentry>
        <indexentry>Listen (use Perception)</indexentry>	
        The character's awareness, acumen and insight.  Perception represents your
        attentiveness to detail and your unflagging vigilance.  In game this value is used
        socially, for reading people and detecting underhanded motives.  Perception modifies
        checks used both for surveying the surrounds for potential avenues of attack, and
  	reduces the likelihood of being surprised, for searching.
      </p>

      <p>
	Perception can be used in social situations to see if a person is being deceptive.
      </p>      
    </abilitydescription>
  </ability>  
  
